Source: duckbotos-branding
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Maintainer: DuckBotOS Team <duckets@duckbotos.dev>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: duckbotos-branding
Architecture: all
Depends: plymouth, gdm3,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: DuckBotOS branding — Plymouth theme, GDM, MOTD, wallpapers
 Provides the DuckBotOS visual identity:
 - Plymouth boot splash screen with DuckBotOS logo
 - GDM theme (login screen with DuckBotOS branding)
 - MOTD (Message of the Day) with DuckBotOS info
 - Desktop wallpaper (DuckBotOS logo on dark background)
 - Shell prompt customization (/etc/profile.d/)
 .
 This package is installed by all modes but is Architecture:all
 so it doesn't affect cross-arch builds.